managers-description =
    FreeSynergy Managers is the unified administration panel for platform-wide resources.

    It is the glue between the Store and individual programs: when you install a
    language pack, icon set, or theme from the Store, the Managers app activates
    it for the platform. No individual program manages these resources directly —
    they delegate to the corresponding manager.

    The Managers panel has five sections: Language, Icons, Cursor, Theme, and
    the Container Service Registry.

managers-features =
    - Language Manager: install language packs, set platform language and locale
    - Icon Manager: install icon sets, set the active icon set per context
    - Cursor Manager: install and activate cursor themes
    - Theme Manager backend: applies theme changes platform-wide
    - Container Registry: view all installed services and their Store registration
    - Inventory view: see the full installed state of all managed resources
    - Node-wide defaults vs. per-user overrides
